      • KvManagerConfig

        public KvManagerConfig​(Context context)
        A constructor used to create a KvManagerConfig instance based on the application context.

        The input parameter context is used to obtain the package name of the caller. By default, the same-account networking is used.

        Parameters:
        context - Indicates the context of the caller's application.
